productAttributes.productDescription: Specifically designed for the iPad Mini. Premium PU leather makes it look noble. The form-fitted design securely holds the iPad Mini in place while the hard-sided exterior provides a sturdy, protective cover. On the back is a large circular cutout to allow the Apple logo to be seen through the case. Fashionably and uniquely designed stand to view for iPad Mini in both portrait and landscape modes. There're two slots on the back of the cover which provide you perfect angles for viewing or typing. Exterior of the case is with a elastic band which holds the case closed when not in use. Allowing access to controls and ports of daily use without removing the case. The installation process is quick, simple, and no iPad Mini disassembly is required.

productAttributes.productDescription: The nCase K6 is a stylishly crafted leather cover for your DOMO Tablet PC with an in-built keyboard. It is designed to give you an added comfort of having a physical QWERTY keyboard for writing those long emails, chatting, or catching up with work in the morning commute, while providing protection from scratches, dents and scrapes. Connecting the keyboard to your device is just a matter of connecting the concealed USB cable from the keyboard into the port of the tablet and you are all ready to fire of those emails, The keyboard is designed to be quite and dust proof. Thoughtfully designed, the case comes with a kick stand at the back to keep the tablet upright while watching videos or keeping it on the table to type using the inbuilt keyboard. The cover flap is magnetic and shuts securely over the tablet. The over-all layout gives you good access to all the ports of the tablet and its leather finish gives you a good grip to hold on to. It's stylish, it's classy and it's functional. Transform the way you carry your world with DOMO nCase K6.
